# Normalize line endings so shell scripts survive a round-trip through
# Windows checkouts. `text=auto` lets git decide per file based on content;
# `*.sh` and `*.bash` are forced to LF so they remain executable on Linux.
*               text=auto
*.sh            text eol=lf
*.bash          text eol=lf

# PowerShell scripts are CRLF-native; leave them as-is.
*.ps1           text eol=crlf
